snippet.title: 【DOAXVV】New Venus Release! Introducing Monica
snippet.description:
A new Venus, Monica is here in DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation!
Enjoy a brand-new, exciting, heart-pounding Vacation with a girl aspiring to become a casino dealer!


○Official Site：https://game.doaxvv.com 
○Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/doaxvvstaff/

Game Information
○Title：DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation
○Platform：Windows PC (Steam) 
○Genre：Sports Vacation
○Release Date：10 April 2019 (Wednesday)
○In-game purchases：Free to play/In-game purchases in steam
○hashtag：#DOAXVV
